HTML-Strip-Whitespace version 0.2.0
===================================

This module eliminates redundant whitespace out of HTML code. It should be safe
in the sense that it won't strip whitespace where it matters like in
<pre>...</pre> blocks.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

* The Test::More module.
* The HTML::TokeParser::Simple module.

